  <h2>The Third Annual Expozine Alternative Press Awards!</h2>
  <p>Six prizes were awarded (three in English and three in French), recognizing the best book, comic and zine sold at Expozine. The winners were chosen by an esteemed panel of judges out of the hundreds of publications submitted at Expozine in November.</p>
  <p>The prizes are sponsored by the <a href="http://www.montrealfringe.ca/">Mainline Theatre</a>, <a href="http://www.drawnandquarterly.com/" title="drawn and quarterly">Librairie Drawn and Quarterly</a> (211 Bernard O.) and libraire <a href="mailto:&#x70;&#x6F;&#x72;&#x74;&#x64;&#x65;&#x74;&#x65;&#x74;&#x65;&#x40;&#x76;&#x69;&#x64;&#x65;&#x6F;&#x74;&#x72;&#x6F;&#x6E;&#x2E;&#x63;&#x61;">le Port de T&ecirc;te</a> (262 Mont-Royal O.).</p>
